        <p>When you first install and launch <MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" />, your login user name is captured and stored in the Review tab of the Options dialog (<span class="Emphasis">File &gt; Options</span>). The first two letters of the user name are also stored as your initials. This information is employed whenever you use the track changes and annotations features.</p>
